WEBVTT

00:03:27.763 --> 00:03:32.092
for dose after dose
after dose of antibiotics,

00:03:32.092 --> 00:03:37.915
or you can walk over and say,
"What the hell is in this well?"

00:03:37.915 --> 00:03:41.708
So I began reading everything that
I could get my hands on

00:03:41.708 --> 00:03:44.262
about how exposure to adversity

00:03:44.262 --> 00:03:47.741
affects the developing brains
and bodies of children.

00:03:47.741 --> 00:03:51.646
And then one day,
my colleague walked into my office,

00:03:51.646 --> 00:03:56.060
and he said, "Dr. Burke,
have you seen this?"

00:03:56.900 --> 00:04:00.902
In his hand was a copy
of a research study